# Web UI conventions

## Stack

Vite, React 19, React Router, Mantine 9, Tabler icons. No extra UI libraries.

## Structure

```
web/src/
├── pages/          # Settings, Repositories, Skills, Agents, ArtifactListPage
├── components/     # ArtifactCard, ArtifactCardGrid, artifactRow helpers
└── api/client.ts   # fetch wrapper; JSON Content-Type only when body present
```

## Copy language

- All user-facing UI strings in `web/` (labels, titles, placeholders, alerts, empty states) must be **simple English** only.
- Do not translate the interface to Russian or any other language unless the user explicitly asks for i18n/l10n work.

## UX rules

- **Global** / **Project** icons are mutually exclusive; click applies immediately (no Save button).
- Click active icon → deactivate and remove symlink.
- `defaultProjectPath` from `/api/status` (CLI cwd) is the only project install path; read-only in UI. Saved `projectPath` in config when project is off is kept for symlink removal only.
- Cards: max 480px, grid `auto-fill` in `ArtifactCardGrid`.
- Scope from frontmatter disables toggles; blocked paths (non-symlink exists) disable toggles.

## Dev

`npm run dev` — server :3921 + Vite :5173 with `/api` proxy.
